    "title": "Punishment",
    "illustrator": " Melany Pietersen",
    "writtenby": " Adelheid Marie Bwire",
    "readby": " Darshan Soni",
    "translator": null,
    "level": 2,
    "pages": [
        {
            "text": "Punishment",
            "pagenum": 0,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_00.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_00.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "One day, mama got a lot of fruit.",
            "pagenum": 1,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_01.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_01.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“When can we have some fruit?” we ask. “We will have the fruit tonight,” says mama.",
            "pagenum": 2,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_02.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_02.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "My brother Rahim is greedy. He tastes all the fruit. He eats a lot of it.",
            "pagenum": 3,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_03.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_03.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“Look at what Rahim did!” shouts my little brother. “Rahim is naughty and selfish,” I say.",
            "pagenum": 4,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_04.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_04.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Mother is angry with Rahim.",
            "pagenum": 5,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_05.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_05.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "We are also angry with Rahim. But Rahim is not sorry.",
            "pagenum": 6,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_06.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_06.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“Aren’t you going to punish Rahim?” asks little brother.",
            "pagenum": 7,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_07.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_07.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“Rahim, soon you will be sorry,” warns mama.",
            "pagenum": 8,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_08.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_08.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Rahim starts to feel sick.",
            "pagenum": 9,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_09.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_09.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "“My tummy is so sore,” whispers Rahim.",
            "pagenum": 10,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_10.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_10.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Mama knew this would happen. The fruit is punishing Rahim!",
            "pagenum": 11,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_11.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_11.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Later, Rahim says sorry to us. “I will never be so greedy again,” he promises. And we all believe him.",
            "pagenum": 12,
            "imageSrc": ".//images/0342/0342_12.jpg",
            "audioSrc": ".//audio/en/0342/0342_en_12.mp3"
        }
    ]
}